high_descs: Walk around a kitchen table and go to the shelf in the corner of the room.
Grab a cup from the top shelf.
Walk to the microwave behind you and to your right.
Put the cup in the microwave, then take it out.
Put the cup in the left cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Heat a cup and put it away.

high_descs: Turn around, go to the right and then go straight to the brown shelf up against the wall.
Pick up the white mug from off of the shelf.
Turn around, go straight and then left to face the microwave next to the refrigerator.
Place the cup inside of the microwave, turn it on, then remove the mug from the microwave.
Look up to face the cabinet above the refrigerator.
Open the cabinet to the right of the refrigerator and place the mug inside.
anns.task_desc: Place the microwaved white mug in the cabinet to the right of the refrigerator.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter then turn left and walk to the shelves on the wall in front of you to your right and stand in front of their left side.
Pick up the mug that's in front of you on the top shelf..
Turn left and take a step then turn left and walk to the counter then turn right and walk to the microwave.
Warm the mug in the microwave then take it back out and close the door.
Look up at the cupboards above the microwave.
Open the cupboard directly above the microwave and put the mug up there before closing the door again.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm mug in the cupboard.
